Welcome to the BLACKJACK GAME!

Goal of the game: Have a hand value closer to 21 than the dealer without going over 21.
If your hand exceeds 21, you bust and lose the round.

How to play:
1. After clicking "PLAY BLACKJACK", you will be directed to select your bet amount
**Note on bet requirements: BET CANNOT EXCEED YOUR CURRENT BALANCE

2. Upon clicking "continue", you will be dealt a hand shown to you, with the dealer's hand hidden

3. You can click either "Hit" or "Stand"
    -If you click "Hit", you will be given another card
    -If you click "Stand", the dealers hands is revealed and the game ends

HAPPY GAMBLING and GOOD LUCK (you'll need it)